1
00:00:03,959 --> 00:00:06,999
♫   Nowhere to escape   ♫

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:09,959
♫   No one to rely on   ♫

3
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:14,039
♫   Withdrawing smiles   ♫

4
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:18,878
♫   Never give in   ♫

5
00:00:18,879 --> 00:00:23,959
♫   Forget about one's youth   ♫

6
00:00:25,859 --> 00:00:28,820
♫   I've never been afraid of loneliness when 
 embarking on this journey   ♫

7
00:00:28,820 --> 00:00:31,599
♫   Tears and regrets go hand in hand   ♫

8
00:00:31,599 --> 00:00:34,499
♫   But my heart is still fiery-hot   ♫

9
00:00:34,499 --> 00:00:37,640
♫  To the distance  ♫

10
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:40,918
♫  The miserable past is like a dagger  ♫

11
00:00:40,919 --> 00:00:43,520
♫  Though my wings are broken  ♫

12
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:50,000
♫  I will keep flying  ♫

13
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:56,199
♫  Following the direction of the light  ♫

14
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:58,359
♫  I'll forget you  ♫

15
00:00:58,360 --> 00:01:04,360
♫  The memory shaped my stubbornness  ♫

16
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:07,359
♫  By virtue of the light in the dark night  ♫

17
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:10,318
♫  I'll return it with a long ballad  ♫

18
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:12,379
♫  The river of life is under my feet  ♫

19
00:01:12,379 --> 00:01:17,060
♫  I don't regret my craziness  ♫

